The paper proposes a method for generating natural language answers to stock related questions, which involves analyzing the relationship between keywords in the question and numerical features of a stock. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE) which are also likely sub-categories.
